org.anchoranalysis.image.core.channel.convert.attached.histogram

Class UpperLowerQuantileIntensityFromHistogram

  • Object
    • UpperLowerQuantileIntensityFromHistogram
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChannelConverterAttached<Histogram,UnsignedByteBuffer>

    public class UpperLowerQuantileIntensityFromHistogram
extends Object
implements ChannelConverterAttached<Histogram,UnsignedByteBuffer>
    Converts a Channel to UnsignedByteBuffer by scaling against lower and upper quantiles of the intensity values from a corresponding histogram.

    A scaling-factor may also be applied to each limit.

    Specifically, the range is from scaleLower * calculate_quantile(intensity, quantileLower) to scaleUpper * calculate_quantile(intensity, quantileUpper) across all voxels.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
